title: Gambas
description:
When Joe Mande and his longtime girlfriend Kylie take a trip to Spain, an ill-fated day in Córdoba goes from bad to worse. Featuring Kylie.

Make sure to check out Joe's website joemande.com and follow him on instagram @joemande
